      <img class="svg-image valign" src="/assets/infrastructure.svg" style="width: 128px;">
    </div>
    <div class="col m8 s12">
      <h4>Infrastructure</h4>
      The computer network is the beating heart of any business - Without 
      internet access and file sharing few businesses can function.<br>
      Front Range IT are experts in setting up new networks, and also in 
